# React Native Rules

## FORBIDDEN — will break the app
- `<div>`, `<span>`, `<p>`, `<button>`, `<input>`, `<img>`, `<a>` — use RN primitives
- `StyleSheet.create({})` — use NativeWind `className` instead
- `style={{ ... }}` inline styles — use `className` instead
- `framer-motion` — use `react-native-reanimated`
- `lucide-react` — use `@expo/vector-icons` (Ionicons)
- `useNavigation` with raw string routes — use typed Expo Router `router.push()`
- `import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'` — use `import { Link } from 'expo-router'`

## Required primitives
| Web | React Native |
|-----|-------------|
| `<div>` | `<View>` |
| `<p>`, `<span>` | `<Text>` |
| `<button>` | `<Pressable>` |
| `<input>` | `<TextInput>` |
| `<ul>/<li>` | `<FlatList>` or `<ScrollView>` |
| `<img>` | `<Image>` from react-native |

## NativeWind patterns
```tsx
// ✅ Correct
<View className="flex-1 bg-slate-900 px-5">
  <Text className="text-white font-bold text-xl">Hello</Text>
  <Pressable className="bg-blue-600 rounded-xl py-3 active:bg-blue-700">
    <Text className="text-white text-center font-semibold">Press</Text>
  </Pressable>
</View>

// ❌ Wrong
<div style={{ flex: 1, backgroundColor: '#0f172a' }}>
  <span style={{ color: 'white', fontWeight: 'bold' }}>Hello</span>
</div>
```

## Import aliases
- `@shared/*` → `packages/shared/src/*` (types, schemas, constants)
- `@ui/*` → `packages/ui/src/*` (shared components)
- `@/*` → `apps/mobile/src/*` (local components, hooks, stores, services)

## File locations
- Route files: `apps/mobile/app/**/*.tsx`
- Components: `apps/mobile/src/components/`
- Zustand stores: `apps/mobile/src/store/`
- Custom hooks: `apps/mobile/src/hooks/`
- Supabase services: `apps/mobile/src/services/`
